```


:::

```{.r .cell-code}
packageVersion("ggcyto")
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[1] '1.39.4'
```


:::

```{.r .cell-code}
packageVersion("openCyto")
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[1] '2.22.0'
```


:::

```{.r .cell-code}
